        <section class="gem-c-notice gem-c-notice--bottom-margin" aria-label="Notice" role="region">
      <span class="gem-c-notice__title">This consultation has concluded</span>


      

  </section>



      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Detail of outcome</h2>

      <div class="consultation-outcome-detail">
        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>We have reviewed the responses to the consultation. We have also analysed the impacts that will be brought about by the introduction of next-generation digital tachographs, required by Regulation (EU) 2016/799 Annex 1C.</p>

<p>The EU Regulation will supercede our proposed changes and it would not be sensible to proceed.</p>
</div>
</div>

      </div>



      <section class="original-consultation">
        <header>
          <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="original-consultation-title">Original consultation</h2>

        </header>


    <section class="app-c-banner app-c-banner--grid" aria-label="Notice">
      <h2 class="app-c-banner__title">Summary</h2>
  <p class="app-c-banner__desc">
          Changes to Approved Tachograph Centre approval so centres don't have to offer analogue tachograph calibration, and other rule changes.

  </p>

    <p class="app-c-banner__desc">        This consultation ran from<br></br><span class="consultation-date"><time datetime="2016-10-19T09:30:00.000+01:00">9:30am on 19 October 2016</time> to
        <time datetime="2016-11-09T23:45:00.000+00:00">11:45pm on 9 November 2016</time></span>
</p>
</section>


      </section>


    <div class="consultation-description">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Consultation description</h2>

      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Approved Tachograph Centres (ATCs) install, calibrate and inspect tachographs, which record information about driving time, speed and distance.</p>

<p>This consultation seeks views on:</p>

<ul>
  <li>stopping the requirement for ATCs to offer analogue tachograph calibration</li>
  <li>allowing smaller sites to be used</li>
  <li>making changes to streamline the ATC manual</li>
</ul>

<p>The changes are intended to remove unnecessary burden on centres, so they can improve the service they offer to their customers.</p>
</div>
</div>


